title: Omni Hypnosis Training 165 - Gerald Kein  Regression And Parts T
description:
Program Length
2 hrs. 23 min.


Learn To Help Clients Release Forgotten Emotional Pain Quickly!
This "Live" Two Session Video Shows You How!

* Learn Regression Techniques!
* Learn How To Use Maternal Parts Therapy Techniques!
* Learn Transformational Therapy To Replace Negative Feelings With
* Positive Feelings!
* Learn To Help Your Clients Achieve Forgiveness Necessary For
* Positive Empowerment!

Session 1. In this session, Jerry shows you various regression techniques enabling the client, in this case a teacher and artist, to see how the pain of divorce shut down his artistic creativity and caused serious depression.

Session 2. In this session, you will see how the use of a very maternal technique of parts therapy helped turn feelings of pain and depression into feelings of forgiveness and self love; thus, creating a new beginning and a new life for the client.

Parts therapy combined with powerful regression techniques is a wonderful maternal method to help your client with many deep problems.

If you want to learn many wonderful techniques to rapidly aid your clients in casting off great sadness and confusion, this program is for you!
